====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[bite]]; to [[snap]] at; to [[gnaw]]
#: {{zh-x|一 條 狗 咬-了 他 的 腿。|A dog '''snapped at''' his leg.}}
#: {{zh-x|他 被 響尾蛇 咬-過{guo}。|He had been '''bitten''' by a rattlesnake.}}
# to [[grip]]; to [[bite]]
#: {{zh-x|舊 螺母 咬 得{de}住 扣兒{r} 嗎？|Will an old nut grip?}}
# to [[incriminate]] when [[accused]] or [[interrogated]] {{gl|especially someone innocent}}
#: {{zh-x|他 站 在 被告 席 上，什麼 都 招認，什麼 人 都 咬。|He was in the public dock, confessing everything, '''implicating''' everybody.}}
# to [[articulate]]; to [[pronounce]]
#: {{zh-x|這 個 字 他 咬 得 很 準。|He can '''pronounce''' this word correctly.}}
#* {{RQ:CUV|Judges|12|6|page=319}}
#*: {{zh-q|就 對 他 說、^你 說 示播列．^以法蓮-人、因爲 咬-不-眞 字音、便 說 西-播-列．|they said to him, “Then say Shibboleth,” and he [the Ephraimite] said, “Sibboleth,” for he could not '''pronounce''' it right. (English Standard Version)}}
# to be [[nitpicking]] on words
#: {{zh-x|別 老 咬 住 我 那 句 話 不 放。|Don't keep nagging me about that remark of mine.}}
# to [[close in]] on; to [[advance]] on; to [[press on]] towards
#: {{zh-co|整 場 比賽，比分 咬 得 特別 緊。|Throughout the match, the scores were especially close in on each other.}}
# {{lb|zh|of [[dog]]}} to [[bark]]
#: {{zh-x|雞叫狗咬|words one does not like to hear|lit=roosters crow and dogs bark}}
#: {{zh-co|狗 朝 著[着]{zhe} 門口 的 陌生人 咬 了 幾 聲。|The dog barked a few times toward the stranger at the door.}}
# {{lb|zh|dialectal|including|_|Hokkien}} to [[irritate]] {{gl|the skin}}
# {{lb|zh|dialectal|including|_|Hokkien}} to [[corrode]] {{gl|metals, etc.}}
#: {{zh-co|這 把 刀 長年 埋 在 地下，已經 被 土 咬 壞 了。|This knife has been buried underground for years and has already been corroded by the soil.}}
# {{lb|zh|dialectal Mandarin|Jin}} [[itchy]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien|of insects}} to [[sting]]; to [[bite]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[leave]] a [[sticky]], [[gummy]] [[feeling]] after eating something [[astringent]] {{gl|in one's mouth}}
# {{lb|zh|Mainland|_|Hokkien}} to [[retort]] with a [[countercharge]]; to [[make]] a [[false]] [[countercharge]]
# {{lb|zh|neologism|slang|euphemism}} {{alt form|zh|口交|t=[[oral sex]]; to perform oral sex on}}

